# Instructions for LiveKit Setup:
# 1. Sign up at https://cloud.livekit.io/ (recommended for production)
#    Or self-host: https://docs.livekit.io/home/self-hosting/deployment/
# 2. Create a new project and copy your credentials above
# 3. Configure webhook URL in LiveKit dashboard:
#    - Webhook URL: https://your-backend-url.com/api/webhook/livekit
#    - Enable events: ingress_started, ingress_ended, room_finished
# 4. For local development with webhooks, use ngrok to expose localhost

